Version 0.1.0 (05.09.2018)

- Initial version. Implemented features:
- Adding selection presets at program start as command line parameters
- Adding images using command line parameters and using a dialog window at runtime
- Drawing additional selections on a per-file basis
- Closing images without saving
- Saving current selections for single images and for all images at once.
  This extracts the selections and saves them as separate files alongside the input files.

